headline: 2 Dividend Stocks Growth-Oriented Investors Will Love
summary: Meta Platforms and Booking Holdings started paying dividends last year.  Both are top players in their industries and have tremendous growth prospects.  Two examples in that department are Meta Platforms (NASDAQ: META) and Booking Holdings (NASDAQ: BKNG).
